&lt;h1 id="two-kinds-of-judgement"&gt;Two Kinds of Judgement&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;April 2007&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are two different ways people judge you. Sometimes judging you correctly is the end goal. But there&amp;rsquo;s a second much more common type of judgement where it isn&amp;rsquo;t. We tend to regard all judgements of us as the first type. We&amp;rsquo;d probably be happier if we realized which are and which aren&amp;rsquo;t.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>